        },
        {
          "aliases": [
            "up.colorspace"
          ],
          "description": "Color space for resampling math. None = auto (\"linear\" for most operations).  - \"linear\" — resize in linear light (gamma-correct, default) - \"srgb\" — resize in sRGB gamma space (faster, less correct)  RIAPI: `?down.colorspace=linear` or `?up.colorspace=srgb`",
